factory
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:In NZ very often a dairy factory manufacturing cheese, butter,  and other dairy products. Compare creamery; and contrast the meat industry's works.


Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: Shortened form of "dairy factory", "cheese factory", "butter factory"
